longBusinessSummary: Green Battery Minerals Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of natural resource properties in Canada. It holds 100% interests in the Berkwood graphite project located in the Manicouagan Regional County Municipality, Quebec; and the Stallion gold project, which is located in the northeastern region of the Stikinia geological terrane. The company was formerly known as Goldcore Resources Ltd. and changed its name to Green Battery Minerals Inc. in March 2021. Green Battery Minerals Inc. was incorporated in 1979 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
